If you will allow me to quote Sinatra's My Way; "And now the end is near and so I face the final curtain."


Just a quick note to let you all know that tomorrow, Thursday, March 7th , will be my last day here at Enron as I move further down the alphabet to a credit role at Entergy Corp.  I will forward my new information as it becomes available but for now - you can reach me at 281-360-6998 (Home Phone) and/or tmoran1961@kingwoodcable.com (Home e-mail)


I wish that it could have been a sweeter ride for all of us but it was not in the cards.  I have enjoyed working with you all and am a better person for the experience.


Best of luck to everybody !

Tom Moran


P.S.

Bonus parting points to anyone that knows who wrote "My Way"
